snippet.textDisplay:
I LOVE this song! Well done, I honestly have to say. I looked up a lot of this game as a result, and it seems like a truly brilliant game. It was planned to be translated for a North America release, but that plan was cancelled for some reason. Why, I ask? Why!? D:

...I also heard it has the classic Zelda "You got an item!" sound in it, among other Nintendo sounds. I hear Skip Ltd. likes to refer to classic Nintendo goodies a lot. 

...But all us Americans ever got was Chibi Robo! D:
